{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They want to be in front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And it's like a centipede.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "You just-- and you marched pretty rapidly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We did lose quite a few people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Some of them just gave up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They just had no strength to go on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The place was-- I mean, the distance we covered with one rest stop in the schoolhouse was atrocious.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We ended up on the railroad platform once again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And this time, we were packed in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I do mean packed in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "There was only standing room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "You could hardly breathe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "You were face to face.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "We had people that finally passed away, died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They gave up or gave out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They didn't even sink.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "They didn't even fall down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "We were guarded, because they were open wagons, cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "We were guarded on each wagon by a German soldier with a machine gun pointing down into it, as if we were going to escape.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "You couldn't even move to get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But the unfortunate thing, Allied fighter planes had come by and had mistaken this for a troop carrier because they saw-- and started strafing the whole train.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And we had quite a few casualties.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I happened to, by coincidence, be in the corner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And so I had a, a two-sided protection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "But bullets could have gone through that very easily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "It was a-- well, a nightmare isn't the word.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "We came to another camp which was pronounced closed and could not be unloaded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And we proceeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And we were on that train for six full days before we were unloaded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "We could hardly make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Of the 1,200, I believe it was 360 survivors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "It was considered to be about less than one third.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "We couldn't-- I couldn't straighten out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "I could hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "We had been standing all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
